<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>고딘 Go-Dein - 고객지원</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/user_support.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header id="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="branding">
                <h1><a href="/"><span class="highlight">고딘</span> Go-Dein</a></h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="service">서비스</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="service">유지보수</a>
                            <a href="#">제작상황</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="portfolio">포트폴리오</a></li>
                    <li class="current"><a href="contact">문의하기</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="contact">견적 문의</a>
                            <a href="support">고객지원</a>
                        </div></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <div class="user-menu">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <a href="#" id="user-name"><%= user.name %>님</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="/myinfo">내 정보</a>
                            <a href="/contracts">계약내용</a>
                            <a href="#" id="logout">로그아웃</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="login-button-container">
                        <a href="/login" class="login-btn">로그인</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

    </header>

    <section class="support-section">
        <h2>궁금한 점이 있으신가요?</h2>
        <p>분야별 전문가가 도와드립니다.</p>
        <div class="search-bar">
            <input type="text" placeholder="검색어를 입력하세요.">
            <button>검색</button>
        </div>
        <div class="support-links">
            <div class="support-link">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="원격 지원">
                <a href="#">원격 지원 &gt;</a>
                <p>온라인 원격 지원을 제공합니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="support-link">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="자료실">
                <a href="#">자료실 &gt;</a>
                <p>서비스 이용에 필요한 문서와 자료를 다운받으세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="support-link">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="로그인 없이 연장">
                <a href="#">로그인 없이 연장 &gt;</a>
                <p>로그인 없이 연장할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>고딘 Go-Dein &copy; 2024 | </p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
